## Introducting new CORE
We’re creating a better way for you to submit CORE data; built from the ground up with the user in mind. We’re looking for forward-looking organisations to perfect our new service. 

New CORE is ready to accept your data for 2021/22. Here are a few of the reasons why you might want to start using new CORE today.
