## A service for everybody
Our new service is accessible to all - however you use it - whether that’s on paper, mobile, tablet or using a screen reader and other assistive technology.

You told us the questions are complicated and difficult to understand. By splitting the form into logical sections and using one question per page, we’ve made the content clear and easy to digest.
