## You spoke, we listened
We’ve taken some of your biggest pain points from current CORE and created solutions to make submitting data simpler. 

For example, you told us that current CORE often rejects postcodes. Now, we accept any postcode, even ones for new build properties.

We’ve also relaxed the rules around rent ranges — and made it easier for you to catch any mistakes.
{% endmarkdown %}  
