## We’re enabling new workflows
It’s not just the CORE website we’ve redesigned; the paper form is all new. Of course, the new paper form exactly mirrors the CORE website, so rekeying your data is easy.

What’s more, we’ve now split the form by section - so you  only need to take the questions you want to ask tenants on visits. Really useful when you can part-fill the log using data from your HMS.

Or, if you prefer, leave paper behind and fill CORE from anywhere on your mobile device or tablet.
